    "## **Ticket médio: sexta vs terça (e o % de diferença)**"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 52,
   "id": "71d28341-22d8-4205-8928-554f1b9d67e7",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "Ticket médio por dia da semana:\n",
      "Weekday\n",
      "Friday       23.76\n",
      "Sunday       22.12\n",
      "Monday       21.74\n",
      "Thursday     21.31\n",
      "Saturday     21.21\n",
      "Wednesday    20.86\n",
      "Tuesday      19.51\n",
      "Name: Total, dtype: float64\n",
      "\n",
      "Sexta (Friday): R$ 23.76 | Terça (Tuesday): R$ 19.51\n",
      "Diferença relativa: 21.83% (sexta vs terça)\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "# Criar coluna com dia da semana \n",
    "df['Weekday'] = df['Date'].dt.day_name()\n",
    "\n",
    "# Ticket médio por dia da semana\n",
    "ticket_weekday = df.groupby('Weekday')['Total'].mean()\n",
    "\n",
    "# Como os nomes vêm em inglês, pegamos Tuesday e Friday:\n",
    "tuesday = ticket_weekday.get('Tuesday', None)\n",
    "friday = ticket_weekday.get('Friday', None)\n",
    "\n",
    "if (tuesday is not None) and (friday is not None) and (tuesday != 0):\n",
    "    pct_diff = (friday - tuesday) / tuesday * 100\n",
    "    print(\"Ticket médio por dia da semana:\")\n",
    "    print(ticket_weekday.sort_values(ascending=False).round(2))\n",
    "    print(f\"\\nSexta (Friday): R$ {friday:.2f} | Terça (Tuesday): R$ {tuesday:.2f}\")\n",
    "    print(f\"Diferença relativa: {pct_diff:.2f}% (sexta vs terça)\")\n",
    "else:\n",
    "    print(\"Não foi possível calcular: faltam dados para Tuesday/Friday ou terça = 0.\")"
   ]
